mdRecord.dcterms:title: Bottles and vials
mdRecord.dcterms:description: Empty bottles of various prescriptions. One was filled at Clark & Palin Drugs in Bristol, TN. The prescribing doctor was Fred Vance, MD, a 1945 graduate of the UVA School of Medicine who practiced in Bristol. [original]
Photographed by Claude Moore Health Sciences Library, Historical Collections and Services staff. [original]
